Overview.title: Overview
Overview.heading: Accelerate your development process
Overview.paragraph1: Stop wasting time on repetitive setups! Our pre-built templates bring together tools like Next.js, next-intl, Zustand and more to help you hit the ground running. Focus on building your projects, not setting them up!
Overview.paragraph2: Choose a template, hit `Use Template`, and launch your project in seconds. Simplify your workflow and maximize productivity.
